<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<style type="text/css">
div.shadow {
    position:absolute;
    max-width:45%;
    max-height:45%;
    top:50%;
    left:50%;
    overflow:visible;
}
img.logo {
    position:relative;
    max-width:100%;
    max-height:100%;
    margin-top:-50%;
    margin-left:-50%;
}

div.container4 {
    height: 10em;
    position: relative }
div.container4 p {
    margin: 0;
    background: yellow;
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    margin-right: -50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="shadow">
    <img class="logo" src="http://assets.modeflip.com/ui/qr.jpg" />
</div>
<div class="container4">
    <p>
        请求来自非移动端。请扫描二维码关注并进入MODE FLIP官方主页<br>
        You are not on a mobile device! Please scan QR code and come back from a Mobile
    </p>
</div>
</body>

